overview.en: GEMR aims to create a decentralized financial ecosystem for global users under the existing Internet economic system. By combining financial technology and blockchain technology, it establishes a set of financial infrastructure for value currency storage, circulation and full-scene applications.
overview.zh: GEMR旨在现有互联网经济体系下为全球用户打造去中心化金融生态，通过结合金融科技和区块链技术，建立一套价值货币储藏、流通以及全场景应用的金融基础设施。
